item.title: [HIVE-20988] Wrong results for group by queries with primary key on multiple columns
item.description: If a table has multi column primary key group by optimization ends up removing group by which is semantically incorrect.
item.summary: Wrong results for group by queries with primary key on multiple columns

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
